// ─── Percentage Width Columns ───
## Percentage Widths ##

// 80/20 split
|80 This takes up eighty percent of the width |20> $5.00

// 60/20/20 three column
|60 Description |20> Qty |20> Price
|60 Grilled Chicken Sandwich |20> 2x |20> $25.98

// Partial: one explicit, rest auto
|80 Eighty percent column | Remaining gets the rest

// No trailing pipe needed
| Item name |> $5.00
|80 Description |20> Price

---

// ─── Invalid Percentages (sum > 100 → equal) ───
## Invalid Percentages ##
|200 This is way too wide |20> Falls back to equal
|60 Sixty |60> Plus sixty is over 100

